Package: demogendr
Title: Tools for Exploring Democracy and Gender in Political Leadership
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bryce", "Corbett", , "bccorbet@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Meghana", "Kolar", , "meghanakolar@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Julia", "Aptekar", , "japtekar2024@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Sofia", "Jachno", , "sjach20@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: A tidyverse-style toolkit for exploring relationships
    between democratic governance and gender representation in political
    leadership. The package bundles a combined country-year dataset of
    democracy indicators, executive leadership (presidents and monarchs),
    and women's parliamentary representation, and provides helper
    functions for loading, summarising, and visualising those data.
